// chartIcons.js
/* eslint-disable */
export const chartTypes = [
    "Unknown", "Line", "Bar", "Pie", "Scatter", "GEO_MAP", "Candlestick", "Radar", "Boxplot",
    "Heatmap", "Graph", "Tree", "Treemap", "Sunburst", "Parallel",
    "Sankey", "Funnel", "Gauge", "PictorialBar", "ThemeRiver", "Calendar"
]

export const chartIcons = {
    Unknown: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M12 8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 1.5-2 2-2 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="17" r="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,
    Line: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><polyline points="4,16 8,12 12,14 16,8 20,10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/></svg>`,
    Bar: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="4" y="10" width="2" height="10" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="9" y="6" width="2" height="14" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="14" y="2" width="2" height="18" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="19" y="8" width="2" height="12" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,

    GEO_MAP: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><path d="M12 2C7 2 4 7 4 11c0 5 8 11 8 11s8-6 8-11c0-4-3-9-8-9z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="11" r="3" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,
    Candlestick: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="6" y="7" width="3" height="10" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="15" y="5" width="3" height="14" fill="currentColor"/><line x1="7.5" y1="4" x2="7.5" y2="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="7.5" y1="17" x2="7.5" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="16.5" y1="2" x2="16.5" y2="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="16.5" y1="19" x2="16.5" y2="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,

    Boxplot: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="7" y="7" width="10" height="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Heatmap: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="3" y="3" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.6"/><rect x="15" y="3" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/><rect x="3" y="9" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.8"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="15" y="9" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/><rect x="3" y="15" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/><rect x="9" y="15" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7"/><rect x="15" y="15" width="6" height="6" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.9"/></svg>`,
    Graph: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><circle cx="6" cy="12" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><line x1="6" y1="12" x2="18" y2="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="6" y1="12" x2="18" y2="18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Tree: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><circle cx="12" cy="4" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="6" cy="12" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="18" cy="12" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="12" cy="20" r="2" fill="currentColor"/><line x1="12" y1="6" x2="6" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="6" x2="18" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="6" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="18" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Treemap: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7"/><rect x="13" y="9" width="8" height="8" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="3" y="13" width="8" height="8" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/></svg>`,
    Sunburst: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M12 12 L12 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M12 12 L22 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M12 12 L12 22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M12 12 L2 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Parallel: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><line x1="6" y1="4" x2="6" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="18" y1="4" x2="18" y2="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Sankey: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><path d="M4 6C8 6 8 18 12 18C16 18 16 6 20 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><circle cx="4" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="20" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="12" cy="18" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,
    Funnel: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><polygon points="4,4 20,4 14,12 14,20 10,20 10,12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    Gauge: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><path d="M4 20a8 8 0 1 1 16 0" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`,
    PictorialBar: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="6" y="10" width="3" height="8" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="11" y="6" width="3" height="12" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="16" y="2" width="3" height="16" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="7.5" cy="10" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="12.5" cy="6" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="2" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,
    ThemeRiver: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><path d="M2 20C6 10 18 10 22 20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M2 20C6 14 18 14 22 20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg>`,
    Calendar: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="chart-icon-svg"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><rect x="7" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="11" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="currentColor"/><rect x="15" y="13" width="2" height="2" fill="currentColor"/></svg>`,
}
